reviewText: The animation is ok but the dialog and singing .... Kids won't mind it but it kinda made me run out of the room.  Not high quality.  More like Jr.college project.
Pretty good for an Indi film and a 1st time director, I liked the character that Rob Ashkenas' played very well "D'Britt", I also liked the way it felt like "Miami Vice" good tunes also...
